attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a piece of rashult. He starts with the base frame, then the lower and upper side legs. The bottom grid tray is next, which he places in the middle. The top grid tray is assembled next, followed by the middle grid tray. The middle grid tray is assembled again, and then the student starts on the wheels.
